<h2>Complete Text Input Control</h2>
<p>For full control over mobile text input behavior, combine <code>autocorrect</code> with <a href="/docs/attributes/autocapitalize/"><code>autocapitalize</code></a> and <a href="/docs/attributes/spellcheck/"><code>spellcheck</code></a>. Each controls a different aspect of the text assistance pipeline:</p>

<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Controls</th><th>Visual Indicator</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>autocorrect</code></td><td>Silent replacement of "typos" with dictionary words</td><td>None (corrections happen automatically)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>autocapitalize</code></td><td>Automatic uppercase on the first letter of sentences, words, or all characters</td><td>Keyboard Shift state</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>spellcheck</code></td><td>Red underlines on words not in the dictionary</td><td>Wavy underlines</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

